{"head":{"layout":"RulePage","next":"/user-guide/rules/comment-word-blacklist/","prev":"/user-guide/rules/at-rule-no-vendor-prefix/","description":"at-rule-whitelist Specify a whitelist of allowed at-rules. Options array|string: \\[\"array\", \"of\", \"unprefixed\", \"at-rules\"]|\"at-rule\"…","title":""},"body":"<h1 id=\"at-rule-whitelist\"><a href=\"#at-rule-whitelist\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>at-rule-whitelist</h1>\n<p>Specify a whitelist of allowed at-rules.</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs   language-css\">    @<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">keyframes</span> name {}\n<span class=\"hljs-comment\">/** ↑\n * At-rules like this */</span></code></pre>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"#options\">Options</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h2 id=\"options\"><a href=\"#options\" class=\"phenomic-HeadingAnchor\">#</a>Options</h2>\n<p><code>array|string</code>: <code>[\"array\", \"of\", \"unprefixed\", \"at-rules\"]|\"at-rule\"</code></p>\n<p>Given:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs language-js\">[<span class=\"hljs-string\">\"extend\"</span>, <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"keyframes\"</span>]</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">import</span> <span class=\"hljs-string\">\"path/to/file.css\"</span>;</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs  invalid-pattern language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">media</span> screen and (max-width: <span class=\"hljs-number\">1024px</span>) {\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">display</span>: none; }\n}</code></pre>\n<p>The following patterns are <em>not</em> considered violations:</p>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\"><span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">a</span> { @extend placeholder; }</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">keyframes</span> name {\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">from</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span>; }\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">to</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">20px</span>; }\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\">@<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">KEYFRAMES</span> name {\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">from</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span>; }\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">to</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">20px</span>; }\n}</code></pre>\n<pre><code class=\"hljs valid-pattern  language-css\">@-<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">moz</span>-<span class=\"hljs-keyword\">keyframes</span> name {\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">from</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">10px</span>; }\n  <span class=\"hljs-selector-tag\">to</span> { <span class=\"hljs-attribute\">top</span>: <span class=\"hljs-number\">20px</span>; }\n}</code></pre>\n","__filename":"user-guide/rules/at-rule-whitelist.md","__url":"/user-guide/rules/at-rule-whitelist/","__resourceUrl":"/user-guide/rules/at-rule-whitelist/index.html","__dataUrl":"/user-guide/rules/at-rule-whitelist/index.html.9c27e29fddc95632071c55fe0528d18e.json"}